{"tid":1590402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回帶： 韋華高槍走火","createTime":"2019-09-23T16:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T16:47:17.000Z","uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d283fc09d3e84b68efa13ba9a6c6c9e572bef79c","tid":1590402,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"警隊洋總督察佩槍走火<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120114/photo/0114-00176-033b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120114%2Fphoto%2F0114-00176-033b1.jpg&h=8392733c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾偵破已故富商李寶椿男孫被綁架案的警隊外籍總督察韋華高，竟然老貓燒鬚。前晚他在馬鞍山大洞村寓所為佩槍退膛時意外走火，子彈斜射落地面，幸無人受傷，警方已檢走出事的九毫米半自動曲尺手槍進行化驗，調查是否涉及人為疏忽。今次是警隊○七年換槍以來，第二次有警務人員在寓所內發生佩槍走火事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120114/00176_033.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120114%2F00176_033.html&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=23e4e49d\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120114/00176_033.html</a>"},{"pid":"585a140280b276f53ea9d7d4a4a167e7747bdefb","tid":1590402,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"}]}